{"tid":141680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟正字重要定明個意思就得？","createTime":"2017-03-03T06:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T09:54:14.000Z","uid":15740,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"682c201c6447509eb0eb7f7d9fd3350c0ba7bd2c","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？"},{"pid":"6bbe3aa481026b35fb1179a912848939ecd110bc","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"認真post 沒人理"},{"pid":"bb910c833dae16332180a21910403808af8ea883","tid":141680,"uid":70912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n<br />\n利申：諗唔透用Agree(正字) 定 Agger(明意思)"},{"pid":"bdfa9207d25001d0c6a4f776915329ec1bf9a5a7","tid":141680,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n絕對係, D 禾系甘牙 都唔知做乜鳩同埋小學畢業未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文盲咁，字都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\nAgree 打做 Agger 其實就係笑鳩 D 文盲打錯字<br />\n<br />\n有人真心以為 BTW 係 Between 唔係 by the way 添啦<br />\n<br />\n正字係幾撚緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebb7aea2838d659a00d2489a7a9ffc97c40f704","tid":141680,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/05/26/10817_20160526022147_5745ed3b8ad27.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F05%2F26%2F10817_20160526022147_5745ed3b8ad27.gif&h=fa62dd4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb85c71720c154c33fff64836aa6cc7ef62d9e74","tid":141680,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真post 沒人理</blockquote><br />\npost(明意思)，thread(正字)"},{"pid":"077955781c01f0395babd2f1ede52ad7e10bfa28","tid":141680,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真post 沒人理</blockquote><br />\npost(明意思)，thread(正字)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11946ad1b85d7ae17f204b957f87540ba0fa52c8","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n絕對係, D 禾系甘牙 都唔知做乜鳩同埋小學畢業未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文盲咁，字都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\nAgree 打做 Agger 其實就係笑鳩 D 文盲打錯字<br />\n<br />\n有人真心以為 BTW 係 Between 唔係 by the way 添啦<br />\n<br />\n正字係幾撚緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 以為連登沒知音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感動"},{"pid":"44051d154b524e0537135fb98affb38a79197e7b","tid":141680,"uid":88717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n絕對係, D 禾系甘牙 都唔知做乜鳩同埋小學畢業未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文盲咁，字都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\nAgree 打做 Agger 其實就係笑鳩 D 文盲打錯字<br />\n<br />\n有人真心以為 BTW 係 Between 唔係 by the way 添啦<br />\n<br />\n正字係幾撚緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中哂point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人同我講話5p字都係廣東話 廣東話本身就只係口語而唔係書面語 所以5p字都冇所謂 因為冇人定正字<br />\n我西咗條粵典link俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1684170b9e0e0a04d7bc71d3cb5716717bed04c0","tid":141680,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"咁你睇得明殘體字咪得囉 做乜要寫正體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057cbdb535e90ac311bd4a3d7b8163fba59f63ab","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n絕對係, D 禾系甘牙 都唔知做乜鳩同埋小學畢業未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文盲咁，字都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\nAgree 打做 Agger 其實就係笑鳩 D 文盲打錯字<br />\n<br />\n有人真心以為 BTW 係 Between 唔係 by the way 添啦<br />\n<br />\n正字係幾撚緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中哂point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人同我講話5p字都係廣東話 廣東話本身就只係口語而唔係書面語 所以5p字都冇所謂 因為冇人定正字<br />\n我西咗條粵典link俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最重要係佢地覺得自己沒錯仲鬧番你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e0e9cd44e0f306da0841015f7fa8d51713fe77","tid":141680,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你睇得明殘體字咪得囉 做乜要寫正體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒"},{"pid":"ad365866667efbfbbe879c691501bd84a6c08dff","tid":141680,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"對於文盲黎講，就明個意思就得；<br />\n對於文明人黎講，就兩樣都仲要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747b9989b7c100f3c7a528a899f18c8338e2a1b2","tid":141680,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於文盲黎講，就明個意思就得；<br />\n對於文明人黎講，就兩樣都仲要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重要，自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542272ce1976f90daa81604f6cf22f89c04cb7fb","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於文盲黎講，就明個意思就得；<br />\n對於文明人黎講，就兩樣都仲要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文果d 又係 tense 錯就話哎呀你明就得啦 <br />\n<br />\n但大佬你錯tense 剩係present past future 已經3個唔同意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecbbbfc2ffdca420e99ff874b4c811a2ef3591b","tid":141680,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"有時明都唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583b0dddbb26f2fb7185c03b32c6534b369772d3","tid":141680,"uid":42476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"成日 質素 都有人打做 質數<br />\n但意思根本唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1b9113634fceb33c37073c5f2081dd86b11bf6","tid":141680,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中英文都係<br />\n<br />\n中文例子： 有人會將根本寫成跟本 但咁只係明其音而不明其意<br />\n有人亦會將己已巳調亂 例如將不能自已寫成不能自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文例如：Hello 有人會打halo, 但halo 根本唔同音唔同解釋<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n係咪我太執著？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打別字既人係間接摧毀繁體字/廣東話<br />\n<br />\n絕對係, D 禾系甘牙 都唔知做乜鳩同埋小學畢業未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文盲咁，字都唔識多隻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Agree 打做 Agger 其實就係笑鳩 D 文盲打錯字</span><br />\n<br />\n有人真心以為 BTW 係 Between 唔係 by the way 添啦<br />\n<br />\n正字係幾撚緊要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個同你講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed377218a15b53d93a78b500c0192933d530302","tid":141680,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於文盲黎講，就明個意思就得；<br />\n對於文明人黎講，就兩樣都仲要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重你老母咩<br />\n文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7f65b551d75ddddbf2a89a60db093e6f974b7f","tid":141680,"uid":81886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"咁/噉為例<br />\n<br />\n有人打「敢」「感」呢類同音但唔啱意思嘅字<br />\n<br />\n有人打「甘」呢類九唔搭八嘅字出嚟<br />\n<br />\n第一類係唔識寫個字但又唔去查<br />\n第二類純粹係同中共治下班農民一樣，唔理意思字型，最緊要筆畫簡單順手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3cd19fbaa01ee60c61c14de61c29da65efa9e5","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁/噉為例<br />\n<br />\n有人打「敢」「感」呢類同音但唔啱意思嘅字<br />\n<br />\n有人打「甘」呢類九唔搭八嘅字出嚟<br />\n<br />\n第一類係唔識寫個字但又唔去查<br />\n第二類純粹係同中共治下班農民一樣，唔理意思字型，最緊要筆畫簡單順手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我成日問自己係唔係太執著 好心提一提佢 喂呢個字係同音 但係係別字 之後佢就會話 「屌 你係認字特警呀？你明咪得囉 得啦知你學歷高有讀書啦 」呢啲令人難受嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638a421aff4da0d38a2ea50bad09688ad0e935ce","tid":141680,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:03:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得明就得，語言嘅作用都係拎嚟溝通啫，分分鐘你依家用緊以為係正字嘅字喺以前係錯字"},{"pid":"f6a8f60963873d3805a7a7bae7869a7a9fad9549","tid":141680,"uid":81886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁/噉為例<br />\n<br />\n有人打「敢」「感」呢類同音但唔啱意思嘅字<br />\n<br />\n有人打「甘」呢類九唔搭八嘅字出嚟<br />\n<br />\n第一類係唔識寫個字但又唔去查<br />\n第二類純粹係同中共治下班農民一樣，唔理意思字型，最緊要筆畫簡單順手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我成日問自己係唔係太執著 好心提一提佢 喂呢個字係同音 但係係別字 之後佢就會話 「屌 你係認字特警呀？你明咪得囉 得啦知你學歷高有讀書啦 」呢啲令人難受嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔認為係要下下捉住晒<br />\n但你明顯係打錯字就要認<br />\n例如：<br />\n成日都見人打「認為」打錯「應為」<br />\n然後其他人提下都唔得，一提就話人正字特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaeea70f241a1e7a73f5d0ed552aedf84116e9f","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得明就得，語言嘅作用都係拎嚟溝通啫，分分鐘你依家用緊以為係正字嘅字喺以前係錯字</blockquote><br />\n我明白語言係用黎溝通 我都認為最緊要溝通到就得 但係有時唔同字真係會有另一個意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如 難道 同難度 已經係完完全全唔同既意思<br />\n<br />\n「難度你唔鍾意我？」 就可能變左係有條友叫難度 佢俾人問係唔係唔鍾意人<br />\n<br />\n「呢隻遊戲我玩開高難道」直頭成句都解唔通添"},{"pid":"b8dbd0788c2cfdb076a2c8fbac3c56b8b6831a7b","tid":141680,"uid":15740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}